3) If the Federal Reserve moves to negative interest rates, then utility
 maximizing individuals will simply hoard cash since it will have a higher
 interest rate (zero) than a negative interest rate.
 As a result, lending will be lower since there will be no incentive to
 lend, simply for individuals to hang onto cash.
\begin_inset Newline newline
